下一代好，這些工作都是值得做</span>，會繼續聽社會的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2361296&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=5b0638bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361296</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"中國政府想做就做，唔係中國人<br />\n<br />\n陳秋實同方斌係武漢被消失左啦"},{"pid":"2e7d5830628168d8d25522106af0d26f533c61b0","tid":2240622,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ur1YEug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fur1YEug.jpg&h=752cda29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6f6803cec05e326cb0380e6dbb7759597585dcb","tid":2240622,"uid":85509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T01:00:01.000Z","msg":"即係如果似大陸咁<br />\n香港會超越大陸幾十萬里<br />\n言下之意<br />\n我淋病叻過維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427c1e582a81c3773746f878371574a106d5c6cb","tid":2240622,"uid":216776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2e7d5830628168d8d25522106af0d26f533c61b0","tid":2240622,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T00:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ur1YEug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fur1YEug.jpg&h=752cda29&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T01:00:35.000Z","msg":"繼續坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44920641df0f506f7ab68f683c75aaee071a0803","tid":2240622,"uid":265731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T01:02:44.000Z","msg":"喺條臭閪眼中，香港下一代全部都係新腥港人，講普通話、寫