972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:02:15.000Z","msg":"林鄭係典型獨裁者思想，本身都有可能做到野，但事實林鄭自己無能無料到但又自視過高，唔講政治，政策都成日擾民無效又失敗，疫情下唔俾堂食結果好多工人冒雨街上食飯已經係一例<br />\n<br />\n最衰係李光耀做得太出色，林鄭以為自己可以做到李光燿呢款獨裁者，但根本唔知自己斤両，佢從來係溫室成長既執行者，同李光耀呢d領導者完全唔同層次，林鄭根本唔知自量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3977373c18cb2738f3ca76f330dc48c41186a7","tid":2240622,"uid":311599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a44c93e8988af55fce1a85278b505a23ced00268","tid":2240622,"uid":192589,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"4aa9a1f53032990d8a5accc52bcb6d705a973adb","tid":2240622,"uid":4285,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T21:46:51.000Z","msg":"香港好似上面咁無規無矩就無今日咁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T23:02:14.000Z","msg":"要平衡，太多規矩就變左內耗，做少少野都好貴，好似大白象工程咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:05:47.000Z","msg":"你on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f39e13a11bc7c5c4c138469d86ac7a4c4665648","tid":2240622,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:06:59.000Z","msg":"林鄭返大陸做省領導咪得囉"},{"pid":"419c2bdea73b509934438036de5713998144ba01","tid":2240622,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea75fc3fec4ffb3ca978b97fd79071397bb19a77","tid":2240622,"uid":275370,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T21:57:23.000Z","msg":"鄭月蛾上深圳比領導屌<br />\n真係好撚偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:09:01.000Z","msg":"柒撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n仲有深圳市領導點點<br />\n<br />\n你問吓佢老細老懵董，煲呔會唔會放佢地在眼內？<br />\n<br />\n689都覺得佢地低級啦"},{"pid":"3ca23a643547668904c7f7824a4935e07623bcd8","tid":2240622,"uid":103654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"佢口中香港下一代就係班外來支那種"},{"pid":"4c7380c0441a6a458a4732f8a51a886c678d57ca","tid":2240622,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime